            <pre id="prompt-sports-1">Create a bold, clean sports team logo for a youth [SPORT TYPE] team named "[TEAM NAME]".

Style:
Strong athletic font with a slight forward slant. Thick solid lettering. Simple underline or swoosh. Optional small icon: [ICON — e.g. baseball, football, cleat, lightning bolt].

Colors:
Primary: [PRIMARY COLOR]
Secondary: [SECONDARY COLOR]

Logo Requirements:
- Transparent background only
- No background color, no mockup, no shirt, no scene
- Remove all extra padding or empty space around the artwork
- Crop tightly to the outer edge of the design
- Center the artwork perfectly
- High resolution, crisp edges, no blur
- Thick, bold outlines — no thin lines
- Crisp, readable text
- Minimal tiny details
- High contrast colors only
- Simple vector-style artwork
- No gradients, shadows, textures, or realistic effects</pre>
